OL,3,CRecord number of children in UK have
OL,4,Cspecial educational needs, new data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FWords by ITV News Producer, Kieran
OL,8,FCarter
OL,10,FA record 1.8 million children in the
OL,11,FUK have special educational needs
OL,12,F(SEN), an increase of 91,400 (5%) on
OL,13,Fthe previous year.
OL,15,FThe latest data released by the
OL,16,FDepartment for Education (DfE) shows a
OL,17,Fcontinuation of a steadily increasing
OL,18,Ftrend since 2016.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
