PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781229799
OL,3,CRecord number of children in UK have
OL,4,Cspecial educational needs, new data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FAmong the figures, 538,500 pupils now
OL,8,Fhave an Education, Health and Care
OL,9,FPlan (EHCP) , an increase of 11.6% on
OL,10,Fthe previous year, and representing 6%
OL,11,Fof all pupils in England, more than
OL,12,Fdouble those recorded ten years ago.
OL,14,FThis rising number comes ahead of
OL,15,Fplanned reforms to the system, which
OL,16,Fhave been widely criticised by parents
OL,17,Fof children with SEN.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781229799
OL,3,CRecord number of children in UK have
OL,4,Cspecial educational needs, new data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FITV News understands EHCP numbers are
OL,8,Fexpected to continue to increase, but
OL,9,Fat a slower rate through to 2029/30 as
OL,10,Fthe government transitions to the new
OL,11,Fsystem. The government believes as
OL,12,Fthese reforms come into effect, it is
OL,13,Fthought the number of children needing
OL,14,Fan EHCP to access support will return
OL,15,Fto regular levels by 2035.
OL,17,FWithin the rising numbers, an
OL,18,Fincreasing disadvantage among pupils
OL,19,Fwith SEN, compared to those without,
OL,20,Fis highlighted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781229799
OL,3,CRecord number of children in UK have
OL,4,Cspecial educational needs, new data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,F45.3% of pupils with an EHC plan, and
OL,8,F39.8% with SEN support, are eligible
OL,9,Ffor free school meals, with just 22.7%
OL,10,Fof all pupils in schools without SEN
OL,11,Fqualifying by contrast.
OL,13,FA DfE spokesperson said the new data
OL,14,Fshowed the growing pressure facing its
OL,15,FSEND (Special Education Needs and
OL,16,FDisabilities) system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781229799
OL,3,CRecord number of children in UK have
OL,4,Cspecial educational needs, new data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,F"These figures lay bare the scale of
OL,8,Fthe challenge we inherited - a SEND
OL,9,Fsystem under immense strain, record
OL,10,Fnumbers of EHCPs, and nearly half of
OL,11,Fthose plans going to disadvantaged
OL,12,Fchildren," the spokesperson said.
OL,14,F"That's why we are investing over #4
OL,15,Fbillion to bring specialist support
OL,16,Fdirectly into schools, to train every
OL,17,Fteacher to better support SEND, and
OL,18,Fgive mainstream settings the expertise
OL,19,Fand resources they need to meet
OL,20,Fchildren's needs earlier and more
OL,21,Feffectively.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781229799
OL,3,CRecord number of children in UK have
OL,4,Cspecial educational needs, new data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,F"We are building a system that
OL,8,Fdelivers for every child in every
OL,9,Fschool, while making sure those who
OL,10,Fneed the most help are never left
OL,11,Fbehind. When schools have the
OL,12,Fexpertise and capacity to support
OL,13,Fchildren facing the greatest barriers,
OL,14,Fevery child benefits."
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
