OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781229799
OL,3,CRecord number of children in UK have
OL,4,Cspecial educational needs, new data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FEchoing the concerns of parents, the
OL,8,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,9,Fdescribed the SEND system as "broken",
OL,10,Fsaying "children's educations and
OL,11,Flives have suffered".
OL,13,FIn February, the government announced
OL,14,Fmajor reforms to the SEND system as
OL,15,Fpart of its schools white paper.
OL,17,FThese included a new tiered support
OL,18,Fstructure, with different levels of
OL,19,Fsupport being given to children with
OL,20,Fvarying degrees of need.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781229799
OL,3,CRecord number of children in UK have
OL,4,Cspecial educational needs, new data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FThe government also intends to replace
OL,8,FEHCPs, the legal mandate for certain
OL,9,Fsupport provisions, for all but the
OL,10,Fmost complex needs.
OL,12,FFrom September 2029, every child with
OL,13,FSEND, not just those with EHCPs, will
OL,14,Falso be entitled to an individual
OL,15,Fsupport plan, though crucially these
OL,16,Fwill not carry the same legal mandate
OL,17,Fas EHCPs provided.
OL,19,FThe government claims these reforms
OL,20,Fare supported by an investment and
OL,21,Fdelivery increase of nearly #8 billion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781229799
OL,3,CRecord number of children in UK have
OL,4,Cspecial educational needs, new data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FThe plans have been met with concern
OL,8,Fby many parents, however, who fear
OL,9,Fthey will lose the legal backing they
OL,10,Fpreviously enjoyed in ensuring their
OL,11,Fchild received the care they were
OL,12,Flegally entitled to.
OL,14,FIt is the failure to deliver these
OL,15,Fplans that has cost local councils so
OL,16,Fmuch in fines and legal tribunals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
