OL,3,CRecord number of children in UK have
OL,4,Cspecial educational needs, new data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FThursday's statistics were coupled
OL,8,Fwith a second release of quarterly
OL,9,Ftribunal figures, which showed the
OL,10,Fnumber of new cases of parents taking
OL,11,Flocal authorities to court had again
OL,12,Fincreased, as had the open court
OL,13,Fcaseload.
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
